</figure><p>大多数情况下，我使用每个移动电源附带的电缆为 Galaxy S22 Ultra 和 iPad Air 充电。对于 iPhone 14 Plus，我使用了 Apple 手机随附的 USB-C 转 Lighting 线缆。对于不包含电缆或包含 USB-C 至 USB-A 电缆的低容量移动电源，我使用<a data-i13n="cpos:23;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5nb25pbWJsZS5jb20vY29sbGVjdGlvbnMvdXNiLWMtY2FibGVzL3Byb2R1Y3RzL3VzYi1jLWNhYmxlLXBvd2Vya25pdCIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiMTE0OWQxOGEtMzY2ZC00MWU3LTljZmEtN2NlNGQwZmQ2ODM1In0&amp;signature=AQAAAWJmFK5yLOrU_OxXHu5r_FfdjuwPrTE0Drz9ZoHY5j4C&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gonimble.com%2Fcollections%2Fusb-c-cables%2Fproducts%2Fusb-c-cable-powerknit">额定功率为 60W 的 USB-C 至 USB-C 电缆</a>。</p><p>作为参考，以下是我们用于测试的每台设备的电池容量：</p><ul><li><p> iPhone 14 Plus：4,325 毫安时</p></li><li><p><a data-i13n="cpos:24;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Samsung Electronics;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=f85e63cd-e13c-4f9d-991c-9fbaadede3ac&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Samsung+Electronics&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAATCYGKJ8oKZ02DVGkVWhFEXn6JEOBDtFsTmJGTTiiGqU&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.samsung.com%2Flevant%2Fsmartphones%2Fgalaxy-s22-ultra%2Fspecs%2F">Galaxy S22 Ultra</a> ：4,855mAh</p></li><li><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:25;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3N1cHBvcnQuYXBwbGUuY29tL2tiL1NQODY2P2xvY2FsZT1lbl9VUyIsImNvbnRlbnRVdWlkIjoiMTE0OWQxOGEtMzY2ZC00MWU3LTljZmEtN2NlNGQwZmQ2ODM1In0&amp;signature=AQAAAdt1WfGqpWCEjE_xZqc37IM7LPmhuoUbnVeXDn4GS6S-&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fsupport.apple.com%2Fkb%2FSP866%3Flocale%3Den_US">iPad Air</a> ：7,729mAh。</p></li></ul><p>我记下了每次收费的时间以及每家银行提供的收费次数。我还关注易用性和整体设计等方面。以下是最佳便携式充电器的评选标准：</p><h2>最佳 MagSafe 兼容电池：Spigen ArcHybrid Mag </h2><p><core-commerce id="f93a356dd8744cc58a3e943d151c8f3e" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p>我进入这一类别时期望苹果自己的<a data-i13n="cpos:26;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAcM2igNiCq6gL9sWMqPRU1uXa_d6XYiG07AszP__-YAC&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FApple-MJWY3AM-A-MagSafe-Battery%2Fdp%2FB099BWY7WT%2F">MagSafe 电池组成</a>为首选。虽然它的表现令人钦佩，在 1 小时 45 分钟内将没电的 14 Plus 充电至约 43%， <a data-i13n="cpos:27;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9TcGlnZW4tQXJjSHlicmlkLU1hZ25ldGljLUNoYXJnaW5nLVdpcmVsZXNzL2RwL0IwOU1KVlhZTUY_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8taXItMjAiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6IjExNDlkMThhLTM2NmQtNDFlNy05Y2ZhLTdjZTRkMGZkNjgzNSJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAUruMmwuSUt4ihTwVIV44mrhkTgzr7MzPY9r2tp8L9Us&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FSpigen-ArcHybrid-Magnetic-Charging-Wireless%2Fdp%2FB09MJVXYMF">但 Spigen 的 ArcHybrid</a>在几乎相同的时间内提供了 56% 的充电。 ArcHybrid 牢固地固定在 MagSafe 环上，并且足够齐平，您可以轻松握住手机并在充电时使用它。与苹果电池不同的是，它有四个指示灯，可以帮助您判断电池组本身还剩多少电量。考虑到 Spigen 的电池比苹果的便宜 30 美元，很容易推荐。</p><p>另外， <a data-i13n="cpos:28;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiI2NmVhNTY3YS1jOTg3LTRjMmUtYTJmZi0wMjkwNGVmZGU2ZWEiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYW1hem9uLmNvbS9ncC9wcm9kdWN0L0IwOU5SRzRHSzM_dGFnPWdkZ3QwYy1wLW8taXItMjAiLCJjb250ZW50VXVpZCI6IjExNDlkMThhLTM2NmQtNDFlNy05Y2ZhLTdjZTRkMGZkNjgzNSJ9&amp;signature=AQAAAWuPZ_3RYcYEmx3XFQgziyupe0FJjwyWL4AmrRy1usQD&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2Fgp%2Fproduct%2FB09NRG4GK3">Anker 的 633 磁性</a>电池凭借其 10,000mAh 的容量提供了更大的电量，在三小时内将 iPhone 电量提升至 100%，剩余电量足以额外充电 29%。虽然支架功能感觉有点用，但电池本身体积很大——但这对于一个两倍于 Spigen 的移动电源来说是可以理解的。最终，ArcHybrid 作为一种快速、便捷的方式在旅途中为 iPhone 进行部分充电，表现得更好。</p><p>值得注意的是，无线充电的效率低于有线充电。我们的测试表明，有线电池组可为设备充电的效率约为 60%。使用无线充电器后，这一比率平均下降至 46%。在权衡能源浪费的生态和金钱成本时需要记住一些事情。</p><p><strong>规格</strong>：5000mAh，最大 7.5W<br><strong>端口</strong>： 1 个 USB-C 输入/输出<br><strong>电缆</strong>：USB-C 至 USB-C<br> <strong>iPhone 充电次数</strong>：0.56<br> <strong>iPhone 充电时间</strong>：1 小时 43 分钟内从 0 充至 56%</p><h2> Best battery for a partial charge on an Android: Anker 511 Power Bank </h2><p><core-commerce id="9d87f8d2665e4e45a215fba54d7b9ee6" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> Until Android phones get <a data-i13n="cpos:29;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/qi-2-charging-borrowed-from-apple-is-coming-to-android-phones-in-2023-114738401.html">something like</a> MagSafe, a wired connection makes the most sense for on-the-go charges. The <a data-i13n="cpos:30;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:Amazon;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=66ea567a-c987-4c2e-a2ff-02904efde6ea&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=Amazon&amp;&amp;signature=AQAAAat2OiJ33b2BJnz34ItI2ULdRBH8zIx1I-D6Z7PX4Vsp&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amazon.com%2FAnker-PowerCore-Charging-Technology-Portable%2Fdp%2FB09NR1SPBV%3Fth%3D1">Anker 511 Power Bank</a> is a cleverly designed unit about the size and shape of a slim stick of butter. The battery has enough capacity to charge a depleted Galaxy S22 Ultra to 75 percent in a little over an hour, so you&#39;ll be covered if you don&#39;t have long between flights to give your phone a bit more juice. It also has a built-in plug and allows for pass-through charging, which means it can act as a wall adapter if you&#39;re ever stuck with both a dead battery bank and phone, but happen to be near an outlet. It doesn&#39;t come with a cable, though, so you&#39;ll need to provide one that can go from the bank&#39;s single USB-C port to your device.</p><p> <strong>Specs</strong> : 5,000 mAh, 10W max<br> <strong>Ports</strong> : One USB-C and wall outlet prongs<br> <strong>Cable</strong> : None<br> <strong>Number of charges Galaxy S22 Ultra</strong> : 0.75<br> <strong>Charge time Galaxy</strong> : 0 to 75% in 1h 7m</p><h2> Best low capacity battery: BioLite Charge 40 PD </h2><p><core-commerce id="9fb13ec7369243b1bb2a076773c71914" data-type="product-list"></core-commerce></p><p> BioLite is probably better known in the outdoor community than the tech world, and it&#39;s fair to say that the <a data-i13n="cpos:31;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:BioLite;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?merchantId=c7108adf-28cd-4cee-8929-a1014adc3d98&amp;siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;merchantName=BioLite&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsInN0b3JlSWQiOiJjNzEwOGFkZi0yOGNkLTRjZWUtODkyOS1hMTAxNGFkYzNkOTgiLCJsYW5kaW5nVXJsIjoiaHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmlvbGl0ZWVuZXJneS5jb20vcHJvZHVjdHMvY2hhcmdlLTQwLVBEIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiIxMTQ5ZDE4YS0zNjZkLTQxZTctOWNmYS03Y2U0ZDBmZDY4MzUifQ&amp;signature=AQAAASr_WKmfS5i4ZbGXbyABmsC4zYdjdQOP5QM6d1hBdp7a&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bioliteenergy.com%2Fproducts%2Fcharge-40-PD">Charge 40 PD</a> is geared more towards camping trips than urban commutes. But this battery simply outperformed the others in its category. The rugged, yellow-accented exterior is a refreshing change from the standard shiny black of many tech accessories. It also has a rubberized finish and feels solid enough to handle the bumps and jolts of riding around in a purse or messenger bag all day. It gave both the iPhone and the Galaxy one and a half charges, which means it&#39;s plenty capable of reviving a dead phone a couple of times when you&#39;re out and about.</p><p> The <a data-i13n="cpos:32;pos:1;elm:affiliate_link;sellerN:;elmt:" href="https://shopping.yahoo.com/rdlw?siteId=us-engadget&amp;pageId=1p-autolink&amp;featureId=text-link&amp;custData=eyJzb3VyY2VOYW1lIjoiV2ViLURlc2t0b3AtVmVyaXpvbiIsImxhbmRpbmdVcmwiOiJodHRwczovL3d3dy5nb25pbWJsZS5jb20vY29sbGVjdGlvbnMvcG9ydGFibGUtYmF0dGVyeS1jaGFyZ2Vycy9wcm9kdWN0cy9jaGFtcC1wb3J0YWJsZS1jaGFyZ2VyIiwiY29udGVudFV1aWQiOiIxMTQ5ZDE4YS0zNjZkLTQxZTctOWNmYS03Y2U0ZDBmZDY4MzUifQ&amp;signature=AQAAAd6EcGyu1V9q1xaUOKOdyi6jJKW4FoemqVdb-iB1Q3x9&amp;gcReferrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.gonimble.com%2Fcollections%2Fportable-battery-chargers%2Fproducts%2Fchamp-portable-charger">Nimble Champ</a> gets an honorary mention here because it&#39;ll also deliver a few reliable fill-ups and comes in a rugged package. It delivered a full charge to the iPhone in two hours plus a 22 percent charge in 16 minutes. It gave the Galaxy a full charge in an hour and 44 minutes, then got the phone from dead to 41 percent in 50 minutes. At the same $60 price point as the BioLite, Nimble gets extra points for being one of the few<a data-i13n="cpos:33;pos:1" href="https://www.bcorporation.net/en-us/find-a-b-corp/company/nimble">B-Corp-certified</a> personal tech manufacturers out there, meaning they&#39;ve committed themselves to higher environmental and social standards, and took the time to prove it through B Lab&#39;s certification process.</p><p> <strong>Specs</strong> : 10,000mAh, 18W max<br> <strong>Ports</strong> : One in/out USB-C, two USB-A out only<br> <strong>Cable</strong> : USB-C to USB-A<br> <strong>Number of charges iPhone 14 Plus</strong> : 1.36<br> <strong>Charge time iPhone</strong> : 0 to 100% in 1h 50m, 0 to 50% in 36m<br> <strong>Number of charges Galaxy S22 Ultra</strong> : 1.33<br> <strong>Charge time Galaxy</strong> : 0 to 100% in 1h 33m, 0 to 50% in